```sql
WITH customer_channels_cte AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel
  FROM (
    SELECT 
      customer_id,
      channel,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at ASC) AS rn
    FROM customer_channels
  ) ranked
  WHERE rn = 1
)
SELECT 
  customer_id,
  channel
FROM customer_channels_cte
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  c.customer_id,
  NULL AS channel
FROM customers c
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM customer_channels cc WHERE cc.customer_id = c.customer_id
)
```

-- 02_revenue_by_channel_and_city.sql
```sql
WITH customer_channels AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel
  FROM (
    SELECT 
      customer_id,
      channel,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at ASC) AS rn
    FROM customer_channels
  ) ranked
  WHERE rn = 1
)
SELECT 
  COALESCE(cc.channel, 'Unknown') AS channel,
  COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown') AS city,
  SUM(t.amount) AS total_revenue,
  COUNT(t.transaction_id) AS transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id) AS unique_customers
FROM transactions t
JOIN customers c ON t.customer_id = c.customer_id
LEFT JOIN customer_channels cc ON c.customer_id = cc.customer_id
LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
GROUP BY COALESCE(cc.channel, 'Unknown'), COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown')
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
```","time":{"start":1771625347179,"end":1771625347179}}}
